data.description: 124 Year old farm house situated on 1.32 acres with fenced yard and large storage building! This 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom historic beauty has many updates including: full bathroom upstairs, refinished hardwood flooring upstairs, fresh interior paint in part of the house, updated appliances and dishwasher in kitchen, smart thermostat downstairs, Windows and vinyl siding just 2 yrs old. Spacious master bedroom upstairs with unbelievable closet space! 2nd master suite downstairs. County taxes only. Outside storage building has concrete floor and electricity. Large  circular driveway. Home is being sold AS IS,
